EXISTING_CODE:
- IntegrationTest.java (src/test/java/com/markdowntoword/IntegrationTest.java) - Has performConversion() helper and basic verification
- ParagraphConverter.java - Contains getTextFromNode() and appendTextFromNode() methods for extracting text from Flexmark AST
